Its a type of fixed Sliding Window

To find maximum sum from a subarray of size k in a array arr

int sum=0;
int mx=Integer.MIN_VALUE;
int i=0, j=0;
while(j<size)
{
    sum=sum+arr[j]; //to move right index
    if(j-i+1<k) j++; //to get to the window size
    else if(j-i+1==k){
        mx=Math.max(mx,sum); //To compare the current sum to max and get more max

        sum=sum-arr[i]; //To move left index
        i++; //move left
        j++; //move right
    }
}


To find minimum sum from a subarray of size k in a array arr

int sum=0;
int mn=Integer.MAX_VALUE;
int i=0, j=0;
while(j<size)
{
    sum=sum+arr[j]; //to move right index
    if(j-i+1<k) j++; //to get to the window size
    else if(j-i+1==k){
        mn=Math.min(mn,sum); //To compare the current sum to max and get more max

        sum=sum-arr[i]; //To move left index
        i++; //move left
        j++; //move right
    }
}